cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Oransim in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "Oransim: Causal Digital Twin for Marketing at Scale"
abstract: "Oransim is an open-source causal digital twin framework for predicting marketing campaign performance using structural causal models, agent-based simulation with large language model personas, and Hawkes-process diffusion forecasting. It provides a platform-agnostic adapter layer with a reference implementation for Xiaohongshu (XHS / RedNote) and extension points for TikTok, Instagram, YouTube Shorts, and Douyin."
